#: ../../mail.rst:397
msgid "Users mailboxes"
msgstr "Caselle di posta utenti"

#: ../../mail.rst:399
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Edit` button allows disabling the :guilabel:`Access to email "
"services` (IMAP, POP3, SMTP/AUTH) for a specific user. Messages delivered to"
" that user's mailbox can be forwarded to multiple external email addresses."
msgstr ""
"Il pulsante :guilabel:`Modifica` consente di disabilitare "
"l':guilabel:`Accesso ai servizi email` (IMAP, POP3, SMTP/AUTH) per un utente"
