msgid ""
"The *automatic aliases for groups mailboxes* are initially disabled. If "
"enabled, addresses like *<groupname>@<domain>* become valid email addresses."
" A specific group address can be disabled and enabled again in a later "
"stage, once Groups mailboxes are enabled. To disable the automatic aliases "
"globally, refer to :ref:`email_mailboxes_settings`."
msgstr ""
"Gli *alias automatici per le caselle di posta dei gruppi* sono inizialmente "
"disabilitati. Se abilitati, gli indirizzi come *<groupname>@<domain>* "
